chapter.para:
  To enable the Xfce Desktop Environment, set

 = true;
 = "xfce";
};

  Optionally, picom can be enabled for nice graphical
  effects, some example settings:

services.picom = {
  enable          = true;
  fade            = true;
  inactiveOpacity = "0.9";
  shadow          = true;
  fadeDelta       = 4;
};

simplesect.para:
  To enable Thunar volume support, put

= true;

  into your configuration.nix.
